title: Episode 14: Grace on Kierkegaard, Idea Formation and Community Participation
description: Today I talk with Grace about her exposer to Kierkegaard, how she's tried to tackle the "big questions" and how to do those things with others. This is one of my favorite conversations so far, so I hope you all enjoy!
